{% comment %}
  snippets/sponsored-ads.liquid
  [2] Dispatcher — routes a single in-feed block to its ad-unit renderer.

  Called from collection-products.liquid once per grid row that has a
  matching block.settings.row. Does no row-matching itself — that stays
  upstream so this snippet can be reused anywhere a single block needs
  rendering (e.g. theme-editor block preview).

  Parameters:
    block       {Object}  required — a section.blocks entry,
                           type "sponsored-products" or "sponsored-brands"
    collection  {Object}  optional — forwarded to sponsored-brands so it
                           can pull products from a merchant-picked
                           collection when source_mode == "collection"

  Children:
    snippets/sponsored-products.liquid
    snippets/sponsored-brands.liquid

  CSS: sponsored-ads.css — shared chrome (Sponsored label, card frame,
                            rating row, CTA button) used by both children
{% endcomment %}

{%- case block.type -%}

  {%- when 'sponsored-products' -%}
    {%- render 'sponsored-products', block: block -%}

  {%- when 'sponsored-brands' -%}
    {%- render 'sponsored-brands', block: block, collection: collection -%}

{%- endcase -%}